{"Id":486,"LanguageCodes":["zh","zho"],"Name":"zho-mazhonggang","Author":"Ma Zhong Gang","Language":"Chinese(simplified)","Description":"Chinese(simplified)","Direction":"ltr","Source":"https://alquran.cloud/api","Translations":[{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":24,"Text":"他将说：“要是我[在尘世时]曾为我的生命做些善事多好啊！”"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":25,"Text":"在那日，任何人的刑罚都不像他[安拉]的刑罚，"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":26,"Text":"任何人的束缚都不像他的束缚。"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":27,"Text":"[有话声对敬畏者说]：“安静的心灵啊！"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":28,"Text":"你喜悦、受[主]喜悦地归于你的主吧！"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":29,"Text":"你进入我的[受尊敬的]仆人中吧！"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":30,"Text":"你进入我的乐园吧！”"},{"SurahNumber":90,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"我以这座城市[麦加]发誓，"},{"SurahNumber":90,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"你在此城中是不受约束的[攻克麦加时，你在此城中惩罚伊斯兰的敌人是无罪的]。"},{"SurahNumber":90,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"以父亲[如阿丹圣人]及所生的后代发誓，"},{"SurahNumber":90,"VerseNumber":4,"Text":"我确已把人创造于辛劳中。"},{"SurahNumber":90,"VerseNumber":5,"Text":"难道他以为绝没有人能管制他吗？"},{"SurahNumber":90,"VerseNumber":6,"Text":"他[自夸地]说：“我已挥霍了大量财富！”"},{"SurahNumber":90,"VerseNumber":7,"Text":"难道他以为没有人能看见他吗？"},{"SurahNumber":90,"VerseNumber":8,"Text":"难道我没有为他创造两只眼睛、"},{"SurahNumber":90,"VerseNumber":9,"Text":"一条舌头和两片嘴唇，"},{"SurahNumber":90,"VerseNumber":10,"Text":"并指示他[善与恶]两条明道吗？"},{"SurahNumber":90,"VerseNumber":11,"Text":"但他没有努力走上坡路。"},{"SurahNumber":90,"VerseNumber":12,"Text":"你怎能知道上坡路是什么？"},{"SurahNumber":90,"VerseNumber":13,"Text":"那就是释放奴隶，"},{"SurahNumber":90,"VerseNumber":14,"Text":"—"},{"SurahNumber":90,"VerseNumber":15,"Text":"或在饥荒日接济亲戚的孤儿，"},{"SurahNumber":90,"VerseNumber":16,"Text":"或穷困的贫民，"},{"SurahNumber":90,"VerseNumber":17,"Text":"但他应该是信士，以坚忍劝勉，以慈悯互励。"},{"SurahNumber":90,"VerseNumber":18,"Text":"这些人是右手边的人[乐园的居民]。"},{"SurahNumber":90,"VerseNumber":19,"Text":"凡不信仰我的启示者，他们是左手边的人[火狱的犯人]。"},{"SurahNumber":90,"VerseNumber":20,"Text":"他们将被关在火狱里。"}]}